snippet.title: Money heist(English) | Season 1| Episode 1 (part 1) | Professor join the team for Robbery
snippet.description:
Money heist(English) | Season 1| Episode 1 (part 1) | Professor join the team for Robbery

A criminal mastermind who goes by "The Professor" has a plan to pull off the biggest heist in recorded history -- to print billions of euros in the Royal Mint of Spain. To help him carry out the ambitious plan, he recruits eight people with certain abilities and who have nothing to lose. The group of thieves take hostages to aid in their negotiations with the authorities, who strategize to come up with a way to capture The Professor. As more time elapses, the robbers prepare for a showdown with the police.

Bean Painting 
Mr. Bean paints a picture of Teddy, but accidentally splashes some green paint on the wall. snippet.title: Bean at Home | Funny Clips | Mr Bean Official
snippet.description:
Wanted
A case of mistaken identity lands Bean in prison and the escaped convict pretends to be Mr. Bean! The real Bean ends up in prison and makes a teddy with dough while the impostor is forced by Mrs. Wicket to do Rockery except failed to realized that the "Bean" she saw was a fake. Then, when the impostor is fed up on this job, he runs away and goes back to his prison cell and explains to Bean that he was the one who escaped and pretends to be Bean. When he's out of the prison, he shouts "I'm free!" except it attracts the attention of the prison guards.

The Visitor 
A friend named Harry goes for a visit to Mr. Bean's room. Unfortunately for Bean, Harry has different things and also is a gluttonous guy who eats too much, so much that all the food in Bean's fridge is gone. Bean tries to get rid of his friend except his teddy is being stolen so he tries to get it back from Harry. Then, he decides to make him go to a restaurant and orders everything in the menu, and escapes from the bathroom when Harry's not looking. Then, when Harry fails to pay the bill, he is forced to wash the dishes as payment and Bean manages to get his teddy back.

Chocks Away
After Teddy gets torn by a boy's radio-controlled model aeroplane, Mr. Bean decides to get revenge by buying his own model plane. As a girl was trying to buy the last plane in the shop's stock, he throws the girl's doll and manages to buy the plane, except he gets bumped by the guard and finds one part to be missing: the propeller. He goes back to the toy store only to be blocked by the guard but manages to fool him and retrieves the propeller. Bean then flies the plane, with Teddy riding as pilot, and manages to knock down the boy's plane. The boy's father then breaks Bean's remote, while the plane is still in flight, causing the plane to go out of sight. Bean believes he has lost Teddy forever, but then the plane explodes and Teddy is ejected and returns down his chimney.

Hypnotised Bean
Bean attends a hypnotism show. He unwittingly volunteers to be hypnotised; when the hypnotist makes him think he's a dog, he runs away and then back at home chases Scrapper around the garden and the house.

snippet.title: It's Mr Bean | Funny Episodes | Mr Bean Official
snippet.description:
Homeless
Mr Bean hunts for a new home, as Mrs. Wicket has thrown him out. He tries out some lodgings he sees advertised in the paper but the series of attempts failed: First, Bean is appalled when the landlady serves him exotic food that turns out to be crocodile. The next apartment forbids Teddy inside. Then a man gives him a bed-space alongside the home of pigs and chickens. Lastly is the burglar duo's fake house. Bean tries to camp out until a downpour interrupts his sleep. Then, when Bean sees his room for rent, he decides to disguise himself to get back in. When Mrs. Wicket sleepwalks to his room, he carries her back into the room. However, as she awakes, she panics and Bean shows himself, pretends that he attacks the man and throws him out of the window. Mrs. Wicket, thinking that Bean has "subdued" him, welcomes him back.

Supermarrow 
Mr. Bean and the father-and-son compete for the incoming biggest marrow competition. Thanks to the super light lamps, Mr. Bean's marrow grows heavier until the father and son decide to put caterpillars in Bean's marrow. Then, when they see Bean with his marrow, they want to swap their marrow with his but fail to realize that the caterpillars are inside. So Bean convinces the judge that the marrow he's holding is his and wins the trophy dropping the marrow on the old lady.

Bean Shopping
Mr. Bean is locked in a department store overnight and has the time of his life.

Back to School 
When there's no milk for his tea and for teddy, Mr. Bean goes to buy milk. However, instead of parking near the grocery store because of the traffic warden, he parks his car at a nearby school. He is unexpectedly brought in by the principal who mistakes Mr. Bean as the new teacher and is forced to teach a group of juvenile delinquents, but he actually may be a better teacher than he thought.

No Pets
Mr. Bean adopts a dog, then a parrot, then a chameleon, but Mrs. Wicket won't allow for any other pet than Scrapper in her house.

Roadworks
Mr. Bean tries to relax, but with roadworks outside he finds this too difficult. After a few failed attempts, he has an idea to delay the workers so that he can relax but fails to notice steam from a cracked pipe. No Parking
Mr. Bean wants to watch the movie Titanic in the city. Unfortunately, he has serious difficulties finding a parking space.

Green Bean
Mr. Bean's electricity is cut off when Mrs. Wicket sees her electricity bill. But then he has an idea - a wind turbine. When Mrs. Wicket gets her electricity cut off, so she steals the electricity without Bean's permission.

snippet.title: Broken Car | Funny Episodes | Mr Bean Official Cartoon
snippet.description:
Car Trouble
The Mini won't work anymore, so Mr. Bean is forced to sell it to the junkyard. But when Bean leaves his Mini around, the worker removes the oil in his engine and steals it. Later, Mr. Bean buys a hot air balloon and paints it the same color as his car. But when he sees his car on the road, he realizes that it's been stolen, so he has to take it back and succeeds.

Car Wars
The mystery driver of the Reliant Supervan becomes obsessed with revenge after yet another run-in with Mr. Bean of the usual kind.

Caring Bean
When Mrs. Wicket is disabled by Mr. Bean's toy car, he takes care of her but it only messes him up when Mrs. Wicket calls him by ringing the bell unexpectedly. Scrapper messes up his kitchen, and he becomes a slave to her, until he gets fed up with this. While Mrs. Wicket is asleep, Bean puts his toy cars on her chair. The next day, he controls it and she ends up trapped in the shed.

The Visitor
A friend named Harry goes for a visit to Mr. Bean's room. Unfortunately for Bean, Harry has different things and also is a gluttonous guy who eats too much, so much that all the food in Bean's fridge is gone. Bean tries to get rid of his friend except his teddy is being stolen so he tries to get it back from Harry. Then, he decides to make him go to a restaurant and orders everything in the menu, and escapes from the bathroom when Harry's not looking. Then, when Harry fails to pay the bill, he is forced to wash the dishes as payment and Bean manages to get his teddy back.

The burglar duo are arrested yet again but leaves Mrs. Wicket heartbroken.

snippet.title: Ladder Trouble | Funny Episodes | Mr Bean Official
snippet.description:
The Ball 
A tennis ball gets lodged in a drain pipe on a rooftop. After several attempts to dislodge it fail, a concerned neighbour calls the emergency workers when she misjudges Mr. Bean thinking that he's jumping off the building. He managed to get the ball by bouncing on a trampoline. Later, when the father tells Bean to get the ball, he throws an egg by mistake and end up getting chased by the enraged father.

Young Bean
When Mr. Bean steals a slice of Mrs. Wicket's chocolate cake, he runs away but ends up hiding in the attic. Mr. Bean sees the things in his trunk and remembers his young life. After Bean realizes that he's the one responsible for crashing the wedding party of Mrs. Wicket, he tries to return the cake slice but ends up getting caught by her.

Missing Teddy
Teddy gets kidnapped by the burglar duo and transformed into a bunny bear. To save it, Mr. Bean tracks down and thwarts the baddies, and finally removes the socks on the teddy bears' ears and returns them to all the kids.

Dig This
Mr Bean digs a hole in his garden and finds a bomb.

snippet.title: Mr Bean the Animated Series - Cash Machine
snippet.description:
Mr. Bean wants to buy a cupcake, but his wallet is empty, so he has to visit a cash dispenser. As he tries to use it, his card is declined and eventually swallowed by the machine. Bean steals a box of tools from a repairman's truck to unscrew the front of the machine in order to retrieve his card, thereby triggering the cash dispenser's alarm and alerting the police. Bean manages to hide inside the machine before the police officers find him. He then accidentally falls into the vault, finds his card and escapes just as the police officers raid the vault. Bean tries his card again after realising that his note of his PIN was upside down (he was reading it as 1861, but in fact it is 1981). Finally, Bean successfully withdraws the money and buys the cupcake. As Bean drives back home, the police officers mistakenly suspect and arrest the repairman.

snippet.title: You Are Mine Episode 1 (English Dubbed)
snippet.description:
You Are Mine Episode 1
Sen Benimsin Turkish Series (English Dubbed)

Ejder, the heir to Yenilmezler, one of the rich families living in Bursa and Naƒüme who is a successful pianist grew up with his mother's pressure, had loved each other the moment they saw each other. The Series is about their love continuing on a ranch and going into chaos.
Ender And Naƒüme, who met after a traffic accident and fell in love with each other, decide to marry but this marriage is not welcomed by their families. After stepping foot inside the Yenilmezler Ranch, Naƒüme realizes there's a sad story behind every door. After a while when she finds out there's also a secret about Ejder between these walls and she loses faith in her marriage. But she won't give up on her love.

#FOX #SenBenimsin #YouAreMine

In the agency, Vera manages to get the address of the Bobylev family, living in an elite suburban settlement ‚ÄúParadise corner‚Äù, where her friend worked. Vera comes to the settlement and finds her boss‚Äô wife Lena lying in a pool of blood, Lena miscarried. Vera helps Lena and promises to keep silent about what happened. Vera meets Karelskaya, the widow of the late crime novelist. Vera asks her about the previous maid, the old lady warns Vera that she should mind her own business and keep her mouth shut.
At the end of the first day, Vera realizes that everyone in this little piece of paradise has skeletons in their closets.

snippet.title: Flowers for Annie | Yeh hai Aashiqui | Episode 13
snippet.description:
Joe Fernandez was diagnosed with Autism when he was around four years old and Joe's mother Daisy raised him single handed. As he grows, Joe's world comes to revolve around his mother and they share a very close bond. Daisy teaches Joe that what matters most in life is to hold the hand of the person who makes you happy. Daisy dies of illness and Joe is left all alone and that's when his childhood friend Annie comes forward to hold his hand. She makes him happy and he decides never to let go of her hand. As they grow up, Annie's world expands and she makes new friends and finds love elsewhere. But it is Joe who shows her the meaning of true love as he holds her hand when she is betrayed and needs it the most.

snippet.title: Yeh Hai Aashiqui - Episode 36 Official Promo - bindass
snippet.description:
Rachael Lobo always found her father Leonardo aloof and unhappy. One day she accidentally discovers the reason for the same. She comes across some love letters which were written to Leo when he was young, by a girl named Lakshmi. Their relationship however ended and Lakshmi got married to someone else. Rachael now wants to meet Lakshmi and find out what went wrong. As fate would have it, she falls in love with Ayush, who happens to be Lakshmi's son. It's history repeating itself as once again the two families stand face to face while religion plays the dividing factor. Lakshmi, now a widow, is left with the option of letting the children suffer the same fate or stand up for their love and bring the two families together. 

Find out what happens in the official full episode of Yeh Hai Aashiqui this Sunday 29th March at 7 pm.

snippet.title: Wrong Number | Web Series | S01E03 - Call Rejected | Apoorva Arora, Ambrish, Badri & Anjali | RVCJ
snippet.description:
Wrong Number is a story revolving around a hilarious confusion where Karan, a 2nd year engineering student, receives a message from Khushi, a medical student, on his (not so) new number. The catch here is that Karan's new number previously belonged to Rajat, who was Khushi's ex-boyfriend. Rajat broke contact with Khushi after a fight they had around the time when school ended and never contacted her again.  But Khushi never gave up her efforts of contacting him. So now, when this number switch happens, Khushi is under the illusion that she is talking to Rajat whereas it's Karan on the other side.

 In a footage from a wedding they just filmed, the sisters find a drunken confession from the bride's best friend. It turns out she is the groom's ex - and he hasn't told the bride to be. Caught in the moral dilemma of choosing to tell the bride or not, the sisters find themselves on other ends of the argument. Meanwhile, it is revealed that Adhira's father might have a similar secret hidden from everyone. Will the sisters do the morally right thing or the financially right thing? And what is the father's bizarre obsession with knowing who the groom's mom is?

Subscribe to Dice Media here: http://bit.ly/SubToDiceMedia

snippet.title: Dice Media | Home Sweet Office (HSO) | Web Series | S01E05 - Breach of Contract | Season Finale
snippet.description:
- Like Shagun and Adhira, take your business to the next level. Start Selling on Amazon today: http://bit.ly/HSO-Amazon-05
- Find the cookies that suit your taste and body type, just like Adhira and Shagun: http://bit.ly/HSO-Cookies [Use coupon code 'HSO' and save 15% on all orders above 500 INR
- Shop Shagun and Adhira's looks from PipaBella here: http://bit.ly/PB-HSO-Collection

From the makers of Little Things, What The Folks! and Adulting, comes 'Home Sweet Office'. A story of cousins Adhira and Shagun, two highly creative individuals who decide to jump on to the bandwagon and start their own business of candid wedding films and quirky wedding merchandise. Amongst the interesting startup problems they face is the most important one - their buzzing office is right in the middle of their even more bustling upper middle class Baniya home in Delhi. Join us to see what happens when these two worlds collide, every day!

Amazon.in presents Home Sweet Office, powered by Butterfly Ayurveda, in association with Pipa Bella. An original series by Dice Media - A Pocket Aces channel.

Episode 5 - Breach of Contract

Chasing a competitive business pitch to work for a coveted fashion firm, the sisters are again at different sides of a dilemma. The commitment to the new opportunity would be for a minimum two years, which Adhira is reluctant to make at the age of 25. Whereas Shagun, having already quit her high paying corporate job to join this business, sees no harm in seizing the opportunity with open arms. As their argument turns to a fight, we are left wondering if this is in fact the fight to end all fights. Will the sisters come to the same page and work for the pitch? Or will Happily Hitched disband for good?

Subscribe to Dice Media here: http://bit.ly/SubToDiceMedia

snippet.title: Dice Media | Operation MBBS | Web Series | Episode 5 - Recovery ft. Ayush Mehra | Season Finale
snippet.description:
Unacademy presents Operation MBBS

Huma, Nishant and Sakshi gear up for their final exams. As Huma considers whether to cheat or not, the others learn something about her which irreversibly changes her image. 
Meanwhile, Nishant is hell bent on not studying, having renounced the field of medicine after what happened to his father. 
Both of their plans change when faced with an immediate challenge.
#DiceOperationMBBS #AyushMehra #SarahHashmi #AnshulChauhan
